    "manufacturer": "Boral Limited",
    "description": "Envirocrete® concrete is a lower carbon concrete product which complies with AS 1379. It contains supplementary cementitious materials to reduce the portland cement content. Envirocrete® 30% has a minimum portland cement reduction of 30% compared to the GBCA and ISC reference case and Envirocrete® 40% has a minimum portland cement reduction of 40% when compared to the GBCA and ISC reference case. Envirocrete® 30% and 40% are ideal for general applications where high-performance concrete is not required.",
